	   <tr><td colspan=2>Hey all, this is Shimor Savagewolf on the Nameless<br>Im in need of some advice on where to go at lvl 29, preferably to solo. Right now, im camped at the WC druid ring and killing the 2 guards at the toll booth. This works good, except that they both con red on occasion, and they are camped alot. So, anyone know anywhere to go to solo? I'd prefer to stay out of huge zones like loio and the fronteir mountains, because you waste time hunting things down. Im more concerned about exp than loot, but if there's a spot w/ both, plz post it for me. Thx,<br>Shimor Savagewolf<br>29 Halfling Druid<br>Forged Horsemen, <br>on the Nameless<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
